column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/84db464b10036ce5f2d3a6276b2047fd87dec9d8 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
I'd like to have this merged quickly, as it would allow patches like #2418 to be pulltested correctly.\n
